Report Generated: ${reportDate}
For the period: ${reportStartDate} to ${reportEndDate}

Income:
<jx:forEach items="${incomeItems}" var="item" >
${item.name} ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Total Income: ${totalIncome}

Expenses:
<jx:forEach items="${expenseItems}" var="item" >
${item.name} ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Total Expenses: ${totalExpenses}

Net Income: ${netIncome}
